+status: published
+coverImage: /images/articles/heavy-metal-certification-costs.jpg
+excerpt: "Food companies avoiding third-party heavy metal certification face mounting legal, financial, and reputational costs. This analysis reveals the true price of operating unverified in today's regulatory landscape."
+description: "Comprehensive analysis of the economic and regulatory costs facing food companies without credible heavy metal certification, including litigation exposure, regulatory fines, and recall economics."
+keywords:
+  - heavy metal certification
+  - food safety compliance
